thread.title_full: Five9 reviewed by Lea Anne Chin-Loy

author: Lea Anne Chin-Loy
title: Lea Anne Chin-Loy
text: Our company uses Five9 for our outbound sales calls. Their customer service and technical support are top notch. I'm always able to reach someone on the phone easily and they are happy to assist me either walking me through items step by step or taking control and fixing issues for me!
